# 商品

### 新增商品
POST {{baseUrl}}/merchandises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "攻夫",
  "price": 20
}

### 更新商品
PUT {{baseUrl}}/merchandises/61e823fc384e380c90f8fc58
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "稻杰",
  "price": 20,
  "specs": "瓶",
  "productionDate": "2020-5-24",
  "shelfLife": 2,
  "manufacturer": "昆明制药厂"
}
 
### 获取商品信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/merchandises/5edc855dd2fbea16f056b543

### 获取商品列表
